caption:
#PfizerSponsored In a powerful new series of Front Porch Conversations, #PfizerPartner @PatrickDempsey sits down with people impacted by cancer in rural America to discuss how we can help ensure everyone has access to cancer screenings and the care they deserve.

In support of @AmericanCancerSociety’s #ChangeTheOdds initiative, these meaningful discussions shine a light on the unique challenges faced by people in these underserved communities. Tap the link in bio to learn more.

This video is for U.S. residents only and is intended to be viewed as it was originally produced by Pfizer. The information provided is for educational purposes only and is not intended to replace discussions with a healthcare provider.
